dct_title_s: Map of Bay Head, Ocean County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: This map shows the Bay Head section of Long Beach Island from Bay Place/Herbert Street to Bay Head Junction. It depicts property plots for the majority of included streets.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Writing is not very legible. Scale of feet is inferred.
